Eipotuoki Isiraeli meirridu


1  Entoning ele rorei lajo nanu te nkishirata te nkaraki intae na aji e Israel: 
2  “Etabatate nemeigil ae kata adumunye ina selenkei e Israel; eiturrayioki te nkop enye nemeetae olodumu ninye.”


3  Amu nji ejo Olaitoriani Enkai: “Ore enkanasa napukunye iltung'ana enkalifu nabo iip ake ooleku, ore ina napukunye iltung'ana iip, tomon ake oolekaki enkaji e Israel.” 
4  Amu nji ejoki Olaitoriani enkaji e Israel: “Eng'oruaki nanu pee ipokipoko; 
5  kake eming'oruru intae Betel, nimijing'ijing'i Gilgal aashu idung'udung'u aapuo Beer-sheba; amu meeta nchere melo Gilgal eyararoto, naa keaku Betel entoki nemeetae.”


6  Eng'orutu Olaitoriani pee ipokipoko, pee melotu ake ninye anaa enkima ajing enkaji e Yosef, nenya ninye nemetii oloar ninye te Betel, 
7  Intae kulo ooibelekeny esipata aaitaa esayiet, nenang'aki esipata enkop! 
8   Ore ilo oitobira Inkokua o Inkapiak uni neibelekeny enaimin nagut

aitaa enkakenya neitomisimis endama aitaa enkewarie

ilo oipotu nkariak e naiposha

neitashaiki ninche shumata oriong e nkop,

Olaitoriani ninye enkarna enye,


9  ilo oyau enkidaaroto anaa enkiwuang'ata egilunore ilo ogol

neaku kelotu enkidaaroto shumata ine negol.


10  Eiba ninche ilo oisikong'isho te kishomi neinyal ilo oiro esipata. 
11  Neaku ore enkaraki nimbookiki olaisinani enkop nioruru ninye enkano enye, itesheta intae nkajijik oo soito oogueta, kake mibikiekie intae ninche; ituno intae isabibu sidain, kake miokioko enaisho enye. 
12  Amu ayiolo nanu eneba nkitarruorrot inyi o enaba esapuko oo ng'ok inyi, intae ilooibooki enkop olasipani, niyaya ntokitin e ropare, nimbelekenyenye ilo omena aarriny te kishomi. 
13  Neaku ore ilo ng'en negira te nkata naikununo nji; amu enkata e ntorroni.


14  Eng'orutu isidain, mme ntorrok, pee ipokipoko; pee etum Olaitoriani, Enkai oo lororani ataa te nebo intae, anaa enitejo intae. 
15  Embai entorroni, ninyorrurru esupatisho, nintubulaa esupatisho te kishomi; amu eidimayu to Laitoriani, Enkai oo lororani pee eipirisie Enkai olpisiaai le Yosef.


16  Nji naa ejo Olaitoriani, Enkai oo lororani, Olaitoriani: “Ore too nkoitoi pooki kituaak naa keaku enkishirata; ore too nkoitoi pooki nejo ninche, ‘Aha, aha!’ Naa keipotu ninche ilaturok le nkurma meetu aaishir, neyietu lelo arriyiak te nkishirata, 
17  ore too wuejitin pooki oo sabibu naa keaku e nkishirata, amu kaim nanu atua empolos inyi.” Olaitoriani ojo. 
18  Intae lelo oong'uar enkolong o Laitoriani! Kainyoo pee iyieuu intae enkolong o Laitoriani? Enaimin ninye neme ewang'an; 
19  ketiu anaa oltung'ani okuet ailany olng'atuny nenang'are olng'arurumi, aashu elo atua aji neigaraki enkaina enye esuntai neony olasurai ninye. 
20  Aime enaimin enkolong o Laitoriani neme ewang'an, o emisimisi nemewang?


21   “Kaiba nanu namen isiruai linyi nemashipakino lelo turrurri linyi. 
22  Ore hoo nikintaikiki nanu ilasarri linyi oopejori o lasarri le nkurma, mang'amaa nanu ninche, ore lelo asarri linyi le seriani loo nchoo inyi naapir, maning'ore nanu. 
23  Ewaita entung'uayioki nanu enkilepilep oo sinkolioitin linyi; mainining nanu oltoilo loo nkinantani inyi. 
24  Kake enchoo esipata erukunye anaa nkariak nerukunye esupatisho anaa enchorro nemetoyu ae kata. 
25   Amaa eikiyakita apa intae ilasarri o nkishorot to lpurkel too lapa arin artam, naaji e Israel? 
26  Ewaita intae Sakuti olaiguanani linyi, o Kaiwana ina ai inyi o lakira o nkitanyaanyukot inyi apa nintobirakita ate; 
27  neaku kaya nanu intae enchom eyararoto te idia alo Dameski,” Olaitoriani ojo, laa ore enkarna enye naa Enkai oo Lororani.

